y. This title was originally published in 1992.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aCommunist Party. 4aactivism. 4afeminism. 4afeminist theory. 4apolitical culture. 4apolitical science. 4apolitical studies of particular countries and areas. 4aprotest. 4asociology. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Process / Political Advocacy.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052033815940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520338159423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520338159/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles